{
  "stem": "3933.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They send up to a Gestapo man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll never forget this thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was I, my mother-in-law, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my sister-in-law, and two children-- one child.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A boy, David.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we hide in-- they've got a little, small room-- it's like a storage room-- a dark, little room.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My Brother-in-law's apartment was a nice one, but got a little, this was someplace for the cleaning woman.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were, financially, very nicely off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was an engineer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were-- I'll never forget-- we went into this room, all of us, closed the door, and holding-- I was holding my son, and-- David, and he says, sh!",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Sh!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Sh!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were all sitting there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The old lady was a little deaf.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My mother-in-law was a little deaf.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then-- guard-- they walked-- [SPEAKING GERMAN], we hear them, going from room to room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my brother-in-law was an excellent actor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In fact, he was not only Gentile, he was German Gentile-- from Latvia, from Riga.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But he hated the Nazis, naturally, obviously, being married to a Jewish woman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he spoke Yiddish excellent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "His name was Rosenberg-- Edward Rosenberg.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Well-- well-- OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I go back to this, and they left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The second time, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] they was-- they were hidden, the second time, without me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This is another part.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They did catch the old lady.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They took her out, screaming, and they killed her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The old lady disappeared before we-- they survived a little bit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Now, going back to this a minute.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I became pregnant in the new apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I have to shush with my son to speak very-- he didn't realize.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He would say, Mama.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was-- the windows was closed with-- not a window shade, an old bedsheet-- a dark one-- closed the window altogether.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
